"{\"uid\": \"variety.com-2024-tv-global-tom-cruise-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-stunts-1236103080\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Tom Cruisegave the ParisOlympicsclosing ceremony a Hollywood flair when he dove off the top of the Stade de France to mark the handover from the Paris Olympics to the L.A. Games in 2028.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999286123992, \"rank\": 7.111863156469275e-08, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After H.E.R.\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.192312644986051e-38, \"text\": \"H.E.R.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"played the U.S. national anthem, the actor jumped off the roof of the Stade de France - the country's biggest stadium - and landed on stage.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"U.S. national anthem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was welcomed with deafening cheers and greeted by L.A. Mayor Karen Bass, who was handed the Olympic flag by Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo during the bash.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999143060486, \"rank\": 8.046904755255455e-08, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}, {\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then hopped onto a motorcycle with the flag in tow and rode out of the stadium to make the symbolic delivery to L.A. As the Red Hot Chili Peppers' \\\"By the Way\\\" played in the background, Cruise rode down the Paris streets and drove into a plane.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999143060486, \"rank\": 8.046904755255455e-08, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8043186800745946e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a pre-recorded segment, he then parachuted out of the aircraft, landing by the Hollywood sign.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once he touched down at the famous landmark, Cruise attached the five Olympic rings to it.Related Stories'Bad Boy' Co-Creator Ron Leshem: 'The Human Capacity to Feel Compassion and Empathy for Those Who Are Different Is Dying'Emily Watson to Receive Richard Harris Award at British Independent Film Awards  Cruise has been a regular at these summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_Leshem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ron Leshem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_Leshem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_Leshem\"}, {\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Independent_Film_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3000050311379015e-17, \"text\": \"British Independent Film Awards\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Independent_Film_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Independent_Film_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was on the ground for the opening ceremony on July 27 and attended a few competitions along with other stars like Steven Spielberg, Ariana Grande, Sarah Jessica Parker and Matthew Broderick.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.83028772073312e-16, \"text\": \"Steven Spielberg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\"}, {\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jessica_Parker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Jessica Parker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jessica_Parker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jessica_Parker\"}, {\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Broderick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Broderick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Broderick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Broderick\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A day prior, on July 26, hewas named a\\u00a0Knight of the Legion of Honorby\\u00a0France's culture minister Rachida Dati.Popular on Variety  As firstreported byVariety,Billie Eilish,Snoop Doggand theRed Hot Chili Peppersperformed at the L.A. Games' handover festivities, along with Grammy, Oscar and Emmy winnerH.E.R.,\\u00a0who performed the U.S. national anthem.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999698221046635, \"rank\": 2.3132807839463836e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"