\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999286123992, \"rank\": 7.111863156469275e-08, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2222, \"end\": 2226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999995627195905, \"rank\": 4.372803472088694e-07, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also said she wants to replicate the joy she's seen across Paris during these Olympics.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8043186800745946e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheParis Olympics have set a high standardby hosting almost all competitions at iconic landmarks, from the Place de la Concorde, the Eiffel Tower, the Chateau de Versailles and Grand Palais.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.727599092230456e-14, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chateau de Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The blockbuster opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics also took place outdoors for the first time in modern history.\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It ran along the Seine River and featured Lady Gaga and Celine Dion.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2684, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2051521037889286e-41, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch Cruise's stunt below.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"IT'S A BIRD.\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bird_Internet_routing_daemon\", \"score\": 0.9998007136655152, \"rank\": 0.00016333656722709785, \"text\": \"BIRD\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bird_Internet_routing_daemon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bird_Internet_routing_daemon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IT'S A PLANE.\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"IT'S TOM CRUISE!\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd2f#ParisOlympics|#ClosingCeremonypic.twitter.com/5v4j8pOwBF  A Variety and iHeartRadio Podcast  The Business of Entertainment\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2848, \"end\": 2855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.